Mitsui & Co. to Build Solar-Power Plants, Yomiuri Says

-- B y   T a k e h i k o   K u m a k u r a
-- 
2011-07-06T05:51:30Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-06/mitsui-co-to-build-solar-power-plants-yomiuri-says.html
Mitsui & Co. will build solar-power
plants in areas of northern  Japan  devastated by the March 11
earthquake, the Yomiuri newspaper reported, without saying where
it obtained the information. The plants will generate enough
electricity for 30,000 households, the report said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Takehiko Kumakura at 
 tkumakura@bloomberg.net  